[FFFFFF]South Barracks:[-] Gaping hole in ceiling; furnishings in shambles; staircase and trap door leading to roof (see Level 0A, area #1); signs of water damage and rot are prevalent throughout the room; floor creaks & groans when walked upon. A section of floor in this chamber (see map above) is completely rotten from rainwater coming through the holed ceiling. Anyone stepping upon this section of rotted wood has a 2 in 6 chance of falling through the floor to area #5 below and taking 1d6 points of damage 
